  "name": "Investigator's Stratagem",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>You play out battles in your head, allowing you to Strike when the time is right. You gain the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.m0f2B7G9eaaTmhFL]{Devise a Strategem} action; however, when you substitute its result for your attack roll, you can't use your Intelligence modifier in place of your Strength or Dexterity modifier.</p>\n<p>You also can't use your Intelligence modifier on other rolls from abilities that expand Devise a Stratagem, such as the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.Tu1hOEr6Ko9Df54L]{Athletic Strategist} feat.</p>"
